{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"43a2bb3b3e","title":"中共中央关于南京大字报问题的电话通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"34b97d9636","index":0,"year":1976,"month":4,"day":1,"articleId":"43a2bb3b3e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"91736a0628","name":"中共中央通知","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"ca0e96a612","name":"异端思潮","type":"主题"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f50baf89bf","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于南京大字报问题的电话通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e"},{"id":"71596ed191","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席已圈阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e"},{"id":"c7868e659a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）据了解，最近几天，南京出现了矛头指向中央领导同志的大字报、大标语，这是分裂以毛主席为首的党中央，转移批邓大方向的政治事件。你们必须立即采取有效措施，全部覆盖这类大字报、大标语。对有关群众要做好思想工作，要警惕别有用心的人借机扩大事态，进行捣乱，破坏。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e"},{"id":"e0b9d73e34","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）对这次政治事件的幕后策划人，要彻底追查。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e"},{"id":"68bbb8f2c6","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）所谓总理遗言，完全是反革命谣言，必须辟谣，并追查谣言制造者。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e"},{"id":"702f82a356","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）任何人不准冲击铁路。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e"}],"page":{"id":"94b124c0fa","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"43a2bb3b3e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}